>> source: Applied Kitchen
>> serves: 6
>> total time: 30 minutes

Combine @lime{1} juice with lime zest.

Whisk the @unsalted butter{2%Tbsp} and @mayonnaise{1/4%cup} together in a #mixing bowl{} until smooth.

Add the lime juice mixture, @cotija cheese{1/2%cup}, @chipotle powder{3/4%tsp}, @salt{1/4%tsp}, @cilantro{1/4%bunch}, and @paprika{1/4%tsp} to the butter and mayonnaise. Mix well.
